{"tid":1718024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地政總署：二號橋屬政府土地　中大獲授非專用通行權","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T19:01:56.000Z","uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1aa61485c662da6bb69ed2e3ed50d6a353d697","tid":1718024,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過去兩日爆發警民衝突的中文大學「二號橋」，業權問題引起爭議。地政總署回覆本台查詢時表示，香港中文大學受地契管轄，而「二號橋」位於吐露港公路及東鐡線之上的部分，屬於政府土地。根據地契，中文大學作為地段承批人，獲授二號橋的非專用通行權，並須負責「二號橋」的維修保養。<br />\n<br />\n地政總署表示，地契是政府作為土地業主與承租人之間訂立的民事契約，以管轄個別用地的發展及使用。地契條款並不限制或影響任何政府部門或公職人員，根據相關法律而行使的法定權利或權力。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492023-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492023-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=da561a77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492023-20191114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4acecdfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492023-20191114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9fef26835494fef84724de5752517531d665c2f3","tid":1718024,"uid":8441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"政府寧願花心機玩文字遊戲<br />\n<br />\n都唔尊重國際文明社會共識，仲想攻打校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a048ed97f4ee8665393cfb33a621f40413cb7f","tid":1718024,"uid":4739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"咁未封左佢做維修囉"},{"pid":"e09398fbae9a772a27fab3f089cd70fb456c2df0","tid":1718024,"uid":15337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"咁炸左佢囉，反正又唔係中大既"},{"pid":"dec1cc4919bd5e456fc5bad292c2aa9b9d2ae97e","tid":1718024,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83a048ed97f4ee86653